      • Game

        public Game(java.lang.String name,
            int year,
            java.lang.String console,
            boolean inProgress,
            boolean completed,
            long mainLength,
            long mainExtrasLength)
        Constructor. Creates a game object.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the game.
        year - The year the game was released.
        console - The platform the game runs on.
        inProgress - True if the game is currently being played by the user. False otherwise.
        completed - True if the user has completed the game. False otherwise.
        mainLength - The length of time it takea to beat the main game in seconds
        mainExtrasLength - The length of time it takes to beat the main game + extras in seconds
